BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 217.68 750 Td (HOW TO USE THIS PLANNER) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (FOR PARENTS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 699 Td (- Sit with your child for 5-10 minutes each Sunday to plan the week) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 683 Td (- Help them break big projects into small steps) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 667 Td (- Review the planner together each evening \(keep it brief!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 651 Td (- Celebrate effort, not just grades) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 635 Td (- Use the reward system - kids with ADHD need more frequent rewards) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 619 Td (- Sign off each week to show you noticed their work) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 603 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 587 Td (FOR KIDS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 571 Td (- This is YOUR planner - decorate it however you want!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 555 Td (- Write down ALL assignments as soon as you get them) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 539 Td (- Check off each box when you finish something \(so satisfying!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 523 Td (- Use 'Break It Down' for any project that takes more than 1 day) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 507 Td (- Be honest about what is hard - that is how we figure out help) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td (- Remember: ADHD is not about being smart or not smart.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (  Your brain just works DIFFERENTLY. This planner works WITH your brain.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 459 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 443 Td (TIPS FOR ADHD HOMEWORK SUCCESS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 427 Td (1. SAME TIME every day \(build a routine, not willpower\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 411 Td (2. SAME PLACE every day \(remove distractions from that spot\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (3. START with the hardest or least favorite subject FIRST) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (4. Take BREAKS every 15-25 minutes \(set a timer!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 363 Td (5. BODY DOUBLES help - do homework near someone else working) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 347 Td (6. MUSIC without words can help focus \(try lo-fi beats\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 331 Td (7. FIDGET tools are allowed if they help you think) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 315 Td (8. CELEBRATE finishing - you earned that reward!) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
