BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 213.84 750 Td (STUDY TIPS FOR ADHD KIDS) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 740 m 562 740 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 715 Td (YOUR BRAIN IS AWESOME! It just needs the right strategies:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 700 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 685 Td (FOR READING:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 670 Td (- Read out loud or whisper-read \(hearing helps memory\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 655 Td (- Use a ruler or finger to track the line you are on) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 640 Td (- Summarize each paragraph in 1 sentence in the margin) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 625 Td (- Set a timer for 10 minutes, then take a 2-minute break) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 610 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 595 Td (FOR MATH:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 580 Td (- Do problems on graph paper to keep numbers lined up) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 565 Td (- Circle the operation sign before you start each problem) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 550 Td (- Check your work by doing the opposite operation) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 535 Td (- Use colored pencils for different steps) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 520 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 505 Td (FOR WRITING:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 490 Td (- Talk out your ideas first \(record yourself on a phone\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 475 Td (- Use bullet points before writing full sentences) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 460 Td (- Focus on IDEAS first, fix spelling/grammar LAST) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 445 Td (- Write for 5 minutes, break for 2, repeat) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 430 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 415 Td (FOR STUDYING/TESTS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 400 Td (- Make flashcards \(the ACT of making them helps you learn\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 385 Td (- Teach the material to a stuffed animal or pet) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 370 Td (- Use silly songs or rhymes for things you need to memorize) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 355 Td (- Study in short bursts \(15 min\) spread over multiple days) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 340 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 325 Td (FOR STAYING ORGANIZED:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 310 Td (- Use ONE folder or binder \(fewer things to lose\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 295 Td (- Take a photo of the homework board before leaving class) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 280 Td (- Pack your backpack the NIGHT before) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 265 Td (- Put things you need by the door so you cannot forget them) Tj ET

endstream
